{"tid":2290540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[11月18號]美國大選新聞總匯","createTime":"2020-11-18T05:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T05:52:27.000Z","uid":54550,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"7a97fd4e034f55f833878a834d00b57ddd12b660","tid":2290540,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"寫在前面：<br />\nFake News定義 - 扭曲事實報導嘅新聞、作出嚟嘅新聞就係Fake News<br />\n<strong>但係</strong>一啲仍然發展緊嘅事、當未verify需要繼續追查嘅嘢唔係Fake news<br />\n<br />\n而家第四權完全失效，所有有信譽嘅左翼媒體全部淪為Propaganda，向呢個時候我地要得到真相好困難。19有個建議個人覺得幾好，我地可以從發言人嘅身份去判斷呢個消息可信任與否<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">意圖向個帖入面貼leftwing media嗰堆友唔該自動消失</span><br />\n<br />\nDominion最新update<br />\n<br />\n分享新聞者 - Sean Hannity（前CNN現FOX主播，佢亦都有向自己節目入面報導過Dominion嘅新聞)<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://thejeffreylord.com/who-is-peter-neffenger/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthejeffreylord.com%2Fwho-is-peter-neffenger%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b85f5482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thejeffreylord.com/who-is-peter-neffenger/</a><br />\n<br />\n內容摘要 - <br />\n資訊由侵嘅legal team 阿頭Rudy Giuliani向FOX嘅新聞節目入面講<br />\nDominion係極左份子嘅公司，而佢地用嘅軟件係由一間叫Smartmatic嘅公司製造<br />\n呢間公司向27個州入面負責計算選票、同委拉瑞拉及中國嘅關係密切<br />\nSmartmatic由委內瑞拉獨裁者建立，而佢地已經向美國被禁止使用，但係又再次以Subcontractor身份重回美國<br />\nPeter Neffenger係Smartmactic嘅Board of Directors嘅主席，而佢而家係拜登嘅過渡團隊嘅其中一個成員<br />\n<br />\n分享新聞者 - Lincoln Wood 侵團隊三大律師之一<br />\n<br />\nDominion承認與克林頓基金、同Pelosi嘅前職員有連繫<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://www.theepochtimes.com/dominion-confirms-clinton-foundation-donation-pelosi-staffer-link_3582450.html/amp?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theepochtimes.com%2Fdominion-confirms-clinton-foundation-donation-pelosi-staffer-link_3582450.html%2Famp%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=df9b4275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theepochtimes.com/dominion-confirms-clinton-foundation-donation-pelosi-staffer-link_3582450.html/amp?__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n<br />\n內容摘要<br />\n<br />\n1、佢地上星期嘅聲明指出，Dominion同埋Smartmatic呢間公司並無連繫 - <a href=\"https://www.dominionvoting.com/，而侵嘅官方成員則向最近指出呢兩間公司係有連繫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dominionvoting.com%2F%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%BE%B5%E5%98%85%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%89%87%E5%90%91%E6%9C%80%E8%BF%91%E6%8C%87%E5%87%BA%E5%91%A2%E5%85%A9%E9%96%93%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%BF%82%E6%9C%89%E9%80%A3%E7%B9%AB&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=4c8ae9b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dominionvoting.com/，而侵嘅官方成員則向最近指出呢兩間公司係有連繫</a><br />\n2、Dominion承認佢地曾經與克林頓基金會於2014年有過一次性連繫並有捐過錢畀基金會，但該組織並唔係Dominion嘅持份者<br />\n3、Pelosi嘅前職員現為佢地嘅Lobbyist<br />\n4、Sidney Powell指出 Smartmatic同埋Dominion係用嚟偷侵嘅票 並且佢話佢並唔會無的放矢，佢地手有証據証明呢件事，包括從（德國、委內瑞拉）海外操控，亦有數理上嘅exact alogrithm去証明呢件事係由大選前已經設計左呢次舞弊行動<br />\n5、Dominion並沒有回應Sidney Powell嘅指空<br />\n6、Dominion向引用CISA嘅聲明「今次係美國史上最安全大選」嚟指出舞弊指控係完全為假<br />\n7、但係佢地<strong>無透露</strong> Dominion係CISA嘅Election Infrastructure Sector Coordinating Council成員<br />\n8、同時Smartmatic都係其中一個成員，補充資料（CISA官方資料，向Member撳落去可以見到Dominion、Smartmatic同SCYTL都係成員之一)　<a href=\"https://www.cisa.gov/government-facilities-election-infrastructure-charters-and-membership\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cisa.gov%2Fgovernment-facilities-election-infrastructure-charters-and-membership&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=872e0550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cisa.gov/government-facilities-election-infrastructure-charters-and-membership</a><br />\n9、Smartmatic上週聲明仍然話佢地同Dominion並無聯繫<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Georgia 最新update</strong><br />\n<br />\n發言人 - Josh Caplan (BreibartNews嘅Home Page Editor)、RT者Lincoln Wood<br />\n向Fayette County搵到2755張票向Memory card度，呢堆票並無upload過<br />\n<br />\n侵團隊轉發新聞 - <a href=\"https://www.waltontribune.com/article_23fa8af0-290f-11eb-b159-7fbad026ff58.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.waltontribune.com%2Farticle_23fa8af0-290f-11eb-b159-7fbad026ff58.html&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=92c8dabf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.waltontribune.com/article_23fa8af0-290f-11eb-b159-7fbad026ff58.html</a><br />\nWalton County搵到284張票 - 其中176張票係侵嘅票<br />\n<br />\n計埋11月17號向其中一個county搵到嘅missing ballots，當中有1643票係侵票而865張係Biden票，截至目前為止係有三個Missing Ballots<br />\n<br />\nLincoln Wood指控GA州長為收取由Dominion同埋Smartmatic所提供嘅回佣之嫌 ，佢RT左呢條訊息<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lanningkl/status/1328420188543463425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flanningkl%2Fstatus%2F1328420188543463425&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b2bccabc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flanningkl%2Fstatus%2F1328420188543463425&h=13f87bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lanningkl/status/1328420188543463425</a><br />\n佢由11月17號開始不斷狙擊狂tag Georgia州長 有興趣可以上去圍觀 今日仲Tag佢叫佢起身 佢連狀書都upload埋上twitter畀人download<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Wisconsin最新update</strong><br />\n<br />\nWayne County本身並無辦法certify選票，但突然又話Certify，<br />\n(待確認)原因係有成員畀Antifa威脅最後屈服 - 汁: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/stillgray/status/1328870776246661120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstillgray%2Fstatus%2F1328870776246661120&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1ZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=feadf38a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstillgray%2Fstatus%2F1328870776246661120&h=2fa6b42f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/stillgray/status/1328870776246661120</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多<br />\n如果今日仲有任何update會向呢個帖繼續"},{"pid":"24ad7e39e68a1613ddb046dba5a97fe120540843","tid":2290540,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51161070478b15bbce02610efc